title: Bobby Is Allergic To Dogs + Lunchbox Asks For Free Stuff For His “Birthday”
itunes:title: Bobby Is Allergic To Dogs + Lunchbox Asks For Free Stuff For His “Birthday”
description:
Bobby takes a series of allergy tests and determines he’s allergic to dogs and a few other things he loves. Lunchbox goes to businesses and asks for free stuff for his ‘birthday.’ Also, Ryan Seacrest sends Bobby a birthday gift.
